title: The Beatles - Nearly 200 Unreleased Songs
description:
Over the years, I have been downloading as many beatles songs as I can.  I currently have about 3000.  I always looked for their unreleased songs rather than their demos and sessions of songs on the albums.  If this is the same for you, you need not look any further.  

This collection spans from before they were a group (Pre-Beatles) to unreleased rarities from when they were split.  Exactly 191 songs are in this collection.

Only a  few of these are from Anthology.  Anthology is a well-known set of rarities and sessions that is easily available via bittorrent.  

So basically, to possess nearly every beatles album, you need:

The Beatles Discography
The Beatles Anthology (all three discs)
and finally, this torrent.

NOTE:  Not all of these are masters.  Some are very hard to hear the vocals.  But it is still cool to have nearly every single beatles song ever.  ENJOY!

NOTE AGAIN:  Nearly all these songs CAN be found on bittorrent, this is just a well-organized collection of actual songs.  It is NOT for competists who want everything the beatles ever recorded, just fans who want to hear every different song they made.
